##
##

Seiryoku no tsuyoi taifū 12-gō ga Nishinihon o chūshin ni tsuyoi ame o furase, hidoi higai o motarasemashita. 1989-Nen irai (Heisei ni natte kara no), Nihon o osotta taifū no nakade wa, mottomo ōku no shisha, yukue fumei-sha o dasu sanji to narimashita. 9 Tsuki 7-nichi no jiten de, shisha, yukue fumei-sha no kazu wa 106-ri to natte imasu. 

Gisei-sha no kata, sono kazoku no koto o omou to, totemo kokoro ga itamimasu. Nihon wa, rekishi-jō demo, shizen saigai ga totemo ōi kunida to iu koto o, aratamete ninshiki sa se raremasu. Kazukazu no saigai nimokakawarazu, nihonjin no kokoro ni wa ningen wa shizen no ichibuda to iu kangae ga netsuite imasu. Seifuku shiyou to suru node wa naku, kyōzon shiyou to kangaeru nodesu. Shizen saigai ni yoru higai kara, tachinaoru no wa, taihen'na kotodesuga, nihonjin no shizen ni taisuru kankei wa, subarashī monoda to omoimasu.
